text: Guðrún Arnardóttir (born 29 July 1995) is an Icelandic footballer who plays as a defender and has appeared for the Iceland women's national team. ==Career== Arnardóttir has been capped for the Iceland national team, appearing for the team during the 2019 FIFA Women's World Cup qualifying cycle. ==References== ==External links== * * * Category:1995 births Category:Living people Gudrun Arnadottir Gudrun Arnadottir Category:Women's association football defenders Gudrun Arnadottir Gudrun Arnadottir Category:Expatriate footballers in Sweden Gudrun Arnadottir Category:Djurgårdens IF Fotboll (women) players Category:Damallsvenskan players Category:Santa Clara Broncos women's soccer players
title: Guðrún Arnardóttir (footballer)
